Package: achtergrondwaarden
Title: Calculates background threshold concentrations for soil policy
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Job",
           family = "Spijker",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "job.spijker@rivm.nl")
Description: In Dutch soil policy the concept of background threshold concentrations is based on percentile values of soil measurements.  This package contains functions to obtain such values, including confidence intervals.
License: GPL-3
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0), fitdistrplus, boot, ggplot2, magrittr, stringr
Encoding: UTF-8
